headline: Why Trane Technologies (TT) Shares Are Trading Lower Today
summary: Shares of HVAC company Trane (NYSE:TT) fell 2.6% in the afternoon session after the company highlighted a challenging residential market at an investor conference, followed by a price target cut from Jefferies.
